companyName: iShares Currency Hedged MSCI ACWI ex U.S.
description:
The investment seeks to track the investment results of the MSCI ACWI ex USA 100% Hedged to USD Index, an equity benchmark for developed and emerging markets equity stock market performance, excluding the U.S., with the currency risk inherent in the securities included in the index hedged to the U.S. dollar on a monthly basis.
 The fund generally will invest at least 90% of its assets in the component securities (including indirect investments through the underlying fund) and other instruments of the index and in investments that have economic characteristics that are substantially identical to the component securities of the index.
